title: Gulf Coast National Parks and Other Designated Natural Areas
name: Gulf Coast National Parks and Other Designated Natural Areas
description:
This map layer consists of federally owned or administered parks and natural areas within the NOAA designated ESI zone along the Gulf Coast. 

Areas include National Park, Wildlife Refuge, Seashore, Wilderness, Forest, Monument, and Preserve.

Only areas of 640 acres or more are included.
